{"word":"H238 - אָזַן - ʼâzan - aw-zan' - Give ear - காதுகொடு","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong>אָזַן"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong>ʼâzan"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong>aw-zan'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong>Give ear / காதுகொடு"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"வினைச் சொல்."},{"paragraph":"- கவனமாய் கேள் செவி கொடு, கேள்"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"to hear, to listen (in the Hiphil)"},{"paragraph":"1) to hear, to listen, to give ear"},{"paragraph":"2) to be obedient, to hearken"},{"paragraph":"3) to hear or to listen to prayers (used of God)"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>Part(s) of speech:</strong> Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English:</strong> A primitive root; probably to <i>expand</i>; but used only as a denominative from <a href=\"#/H241 - אֹזֶן - ʼôzen - o'-zen/241\">H241</a>; to <i>broaden out the ear</i> (with the hand), that is, (by implication) to <i>listen: - </i>give (perceive by the) ear, hear (-ken). See <a href=\"#/H239 - אָזַן - ʼâzan - aw-zan'/239\">H239</a>."},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"spacer\"></span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H238 - אָזַן - ʼâzan - aw-zan'/238\">H238</a>, <a href=\"#/H240 - אָזֵן - ʼâzên - aw-zane'/240\">H240</a>, <a href=\"#/H241 - אֹזֶן - ʼôzen - o'-zen/241\">H241</a>, <a href=\"#/H243 - אַזְנֹות תָּבֹור - ʼAznôwth Tâbôwr - az-noth' taw-bore'/243\">H243</a>, <a href=\"#/H244 - אׇזְנִי - ʼOznîy - oz-nee'/244\">H244</a>, <a href=\"#/H245 - אֲזַנְיָה - ʼĂzanyâh - az-an-yaw'/245\">H245</a>, <a href=\"#/H2970 - יַאֲזַנְיָה - Yaʼăzanyâh - yah-az-an-yaw'/2970\">H2970</a>, <a href=\"#/H3153 - יְזַנְיָה - Yᵉzanyâh - yez-an-yaw'/3153\">H3153</a>"}]}